WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.000
It's been a long journey,
and it's only fitting for

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.050
it to come full circle back to
where you started, Toy City.

00:00:07.050 --> 00:00:10.540
Feels like only yesterday you were
trudging through messy nested loops to

00:00:10.540 --> 00:00:11.470
help track sales.

00:00:12.470 --> 00:00:14.045
After your most recent proof of concept,

00:00:14.045 --> 00:00:16.710
your boss wants to go all in
with a new inventory system.

00:00:17.940 --> 00:00:20.515
This project will be a coming
together of everything you've in this

00:00:20.515 --> 00:00:22.120
nanodegree program.

00:00:22.120 --> 00:00:27.850
Loops, classes, errors, inheritance,
meta-programming, git, you name it.

00:00:27.850 --> 00:00:28.920
Read on for the details.

